* ============================================================
* J113 N-Channel JFET Model
* Source: LTspice standard.jft (Linear Systems)
*
* Key specs:
*   Vto (pinch-off) = -1.382 V
*   Beta = 9.109 mA/V^2
*   Idss ~ 30 mA
*   Rds(on) ~ 30 ohms at Vgs=0
*   Cgs = 5.74 pF, Cgd = 6.46 pF
*
* Usage in AGC: drain-source as voltage-controlled resistor
*   Vgs = 0    -> Rds ~ 30 ohms
*   Vgs -> Vto -> Rds > 10k ohms
*
* Pins: D G S (drain, gate, source)
* Instance: J1 drain gate source J113
* ============================================================

.model J113 NJF(Beta=9.109m Betatce=-0.5 Vto=-1.382 Vtotc=-2.5m
+ Lambda=8m Is=205.2f Xti=3 Isr=1988f Nr=2 Alpha=20.98u N=1
+ Rd=1 Rs=1 Cgd=6.46p Cgs=5.74p Fc=0.5 Vk=123.7 M=407m Pb=1
+ Kf=12300f Af=1)
